#   item 35 — verification/property_test.c + step [60]: degenerate-input properties over real Shamir.c
#     / KeyslotStore.c (threshold==n, duplicate x-coords -> SHAMIR_ERR_PARAM, range rejection, boundary
#     secrets, zero-length keyslot passwords), built under ASan+UBSan.
#   item 38 — scripts/secrets-scan.sh (pattern-based, dependency-free) + .githooks/pre-commit + a
#     `secrets-scan` CI job + step [61]. --self-test: a planted secret is caught, crypto KAT hex is not.
#   item 37 — .clang-tidy (curated high-signal: clang static analyzer + bugprone subset, WarningsAsErrors)
#     + scripts/clang-tidy-fork.sh + a `clang-tidy` CI job + step [62]; CodeQL in .github/workflows/codeql.yml.
